sources.title: Maysville | Full Movie | Powerful Drama | Russell Hodgkinson
sources.description:
Maysville - A young boy, Teddy Rogers, is devastated by a tragic accident and taken from his family to pay a penance which forces him into a life of hard labor. Four years later he escapes to the town of Maysville, where he finds love and a hopeful future, but is soon hunted and haunted by his past. Teddy must begin to forgive himself and challenge the demons that pursue him in order to find the life he so desperately desires.
2021.  Stars: Russell Hodgkinson, Trin Miller, John Legas
